In our effort to improve your banking experience with DBS digibank, we’ve made the following improvements:
1. Register your Mobile and NRIC/FIN number for PayNow to send and receive funds conveniently
2. Perform same day transfers and enjoy $0 fees with DBS remit to Europe and selected destinations
3. Take a quick look at your credit card statement balance and available limit with Peek Balance
Do continue to provide us your feedback to help us make your banking experience better.

The DBS digibank app includes the following service improvements.:
1. One-click access to PayNow transfers.
2. Register your Mobile and NRIC/FIN number for PayNow to send and receive funds.
3. An added feature in Peek Balance for your Credit Card statement balance and available limit.
We welcome your feedback as we enhance your banking experience
